metadata.name: Sunrise
metadata.description:
Artist: OJ Perry
Attached file: 4611 × 6916 pixels  
File size: 18 MB  
Gear: Nikon z7ii 
Stats: f 5.6 | 1/640 | ISO 200 | 18mm
Date: October 2022

Sunrise is part of the 3-piece NFT collection Tryptychon of Autumn. When exhibited correctly, Sunrise should be shown on the left side of the centerpiece. Sunrise was captured during the morning of October 29, 2022, at Lake Gosau in Austria. 

Bio:  
OJ Perry, based in Vienna, Austria, is a passionate photographer who’s love for photography grew at an early age with a second hand Yashica camera from his dad. OJ has joined the NFT world in summer 2021, selling 1/1s and editions to renown collectors. 

License:  
This NFT can be used to display privately, in (non)commercial settings, in groups with an unlimited number of participants. License includes unlimited use/display in virtual or physical galleries. Provides no rights to create commercial merchandise, commercial distribution, or derivative works.
